Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.75,0:00:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嚮往天空 親近天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.14,0:00:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翱翔於天空的神秘力量開始被一少部分人掌握的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.85,0:00:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Guardian
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.25,0:00:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那裏有一個傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.55,0:00:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在天之邊際雲之彼方存在著一片黃金之地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.72,0:00:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個故事講述了一個追尋夢想自由生存的天空盜賊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.51,0:00:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,空盜團少年——酷的波瀾起伏的愛和冒險的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.61,0:02:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了了結一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.10,0:02:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有與酷分開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.61,0:02:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓苦惱的蕾綻放笑容的卻正是酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.84,0:02:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷和蕾決定不逃避現實 一起去煌珠樂園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.59,0:02:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另一方面希絲卡在兩人身上看到了希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.80,0:02:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始了新的行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.53,0:02:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,躲開ChaosChoir\N的追擊後繼續踏上旅途的酷他們的前方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.26,0:02:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無限神秘的煌珠樂園展現在眼前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.60,0:02:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,此時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.59,0:02:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,離開酷他們的希絲卡獨自返回守護翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.24,0:03:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帶著說服上層避免與煌珠樂園全面開戰的使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.17,0:03:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作為完全保護協會的守護翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.01,0:03:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,挑起與本該保護的煌珠之間的戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.23,0:03:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是決不應該的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.78,0:03:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論如何也要阻止這場戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.13,0:03:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管起因是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.30,0:03:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,克魯斯輔佐官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.72,0:03:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有事要匯報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.99,0:03:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二十三唱 約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.33,0:03:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了 蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.72,0:03:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看上去沒什麼精神啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.33,0:03:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過不要緊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.89,0:03:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都走到這裏了只需最後再加把勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.12,0:03:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.21,0:03:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.37,0:04:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什 什麼啊 突然道謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.00,0:04:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能走到這裏是因為有酷在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.46,0:04:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果沒有酷的話我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.83,0:04:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.90,0:04:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不是約定了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.87,0:04:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「帶蕾去煌珠樂園」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.47,0:04:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能遇到酷真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.08,0:04:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.81,0:04:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在 在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.77,0:04:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.30,0:04:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,守護翼和ChaosChoir
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.41,0:04:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,據內部消息守護翼是發動總攻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.10,0:05:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是說真的打算和ChaosChoir開戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.63,0:05:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在不是說這話的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.23,0:05:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.21,0:05:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.92,0:05:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.10,0:05:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉撒蒂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.92,0:05:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼會在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.46,0:05:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.39,0:05:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.22,0:05:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家冷靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.99,0:05:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重整陣列
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.91,0:05:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.65,0:06:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.33,0:06:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人攻過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.20,0:06:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.06,0:07:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.80,0:07:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.86,0:07:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一次見到伊芙大人這副樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.12,0:07:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊芙大人知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.32,0:07:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾芙麗·梅札蘭斯大人就在附近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.21,0:07:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼辦 歐琺斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.15,0:07:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然不鄭重出迎是不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.12,0:07:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說實話情況很糟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.58,0:07:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛空艇部隊全滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.63,0:07:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地面部隊也是ChaosChoir方面慣於作戰的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.33,0:07:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管是戰鬥力還是指揮能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.02,0:07:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們一邊倒地處於劣勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.93,0:07:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉撒蒂你們為什麼會來這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.45,0:07:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,守護翼發動總攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.09,0:07:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能戰鬥的都被驅使參軍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.12,0:07:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以的話我也不想戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.64,0:08:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 守護翼曾經保護我 對我有恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.15,0:08:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然姐姐要戰鬥那我也一起戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.31,0:08:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要能待在姐姐身邊我就能奮戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.76,0:08:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼想了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.65,0:08:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.14,0:08:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,煌珠互相廝殺真的很痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.59,0:08:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.57,0:08:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ChaosChoir的戰鬥方式太沒人性了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.43,0:08:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們將煌珠用完就拋棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.61,0:08:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果喪失戰鬥能力的話就像廢物一樣拋棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.88,0:08:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐也不能原諒做出這種事的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.80,0:08:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是敵人一個接一個地出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.29,0:08:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都已經到極限了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.22,0:08:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們接下來不知道會怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.37,0:09:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 莉莉雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.47,0:09:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.62,0:09:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.44,0:09:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.43,0:09:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.99,0:09:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們前來迎接您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.79,0:09:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾芙麗·梅札蘭斯大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.41,0:09:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不想制止戰爭嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.26,0:09:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.40,0:09:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 不知道她去哪兒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.17,0:09:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她剛才在河邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.83,0:09:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊 謝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.75,0:10:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想制止這場戰爭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.78,0:10:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你來我們這邊的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.09,0:10:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切都將結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.61,0:10:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.11,0:10:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我去煌珠樂園的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.37,0:10:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.56,0:10:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,汝與我{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.00,0:10:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,情分已盡{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.48,0:10:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋪路向宮{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.16,0:10:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,氣息相應{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.54,0:10:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沉沉睡去{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.80,0:10:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,生命{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.25,0:10:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,於我手中{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.59,0:10:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不再延續{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.65,0:10:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.71,0:10:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.73,0:11:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.74,0:11:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.51,0:11:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.30,0:11:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們對蕾做了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.13,0:11:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也聽到了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.23,0:11:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾芙麗·梅札蘭斯大人也自願選擇來我們這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.21,0:11:16.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.71,0:11:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾不可能那麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.71,0:11:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白癡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.18,0:11:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜拜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.46,0:11:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.38,0:11:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,臥魯克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.36,0:11:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把蕾還給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.51,0:11:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我之去處{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.78,0:11:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不許阻攔{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.18,0:11:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,速速退下{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.91,0:11:51.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.97,0:12:00.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.28,0:12:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.10,0:12:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.77,0:12:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.61,0:12:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你既是蕾的同契者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.88,0:12:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就該理解她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.38,0:12:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她是為了制止戰爭才獨自前往的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.10,0:12:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為敵人的目標是蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.37,0:12:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而她也知道這一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.58,0:12:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這你知道的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.11,0:12:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不想再讓誰受傷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.79,0:12:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼想了那孩子才...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.35,0:12:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.21,0:12:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾不想戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.90,0:12:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總考慮著想做點什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.72,0:12:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 但是我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.07,0:12:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.21,0:13:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被煌珠拋棄的同契者啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.87,0:13:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太可笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.50,0:13:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.41,0:13:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,臥魯說的沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.73,0:13:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被搭檔拋棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.10,0:13:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太丟人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.94,0:13:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.27,0:13:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說什麼就算無需戰鬥也願相伴一生的是誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.99,0:13:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你如果對七煌寶樹死心了的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.36,0:13:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就只有我去奪回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.19,0:13:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.17,0:13:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不中聽的話就好好保護她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.44,0:13:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管對手是我還是他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.05,0:13:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打起精神來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.00,0:13:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,痛苦的不止是你一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.77,0:13:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,臥魯他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.08,0:13:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別多嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.86,0:13:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對 對不起啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.41,0:14:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來這裏的目的可能落空了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.03,0:14:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,七煌寶樹既然已經去了煌珠樂園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.60,0:14:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這場戰爭也就快結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.25,0:14:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.29,0:14:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.40,0:14:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,福音的最終樂章還沒響起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.36,0:14:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.99,0:14:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然是個令人不爽的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.81,0:14:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我和他意見一致
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.76,0:14:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉撒蒂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.41,0:14:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣子不像你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.04,0:14:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我所認識的酷德·望·朱魯愛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.14,0:14:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還未想好就已行動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.50,0:14:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我這是在做什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.53,0:14:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明很理解酷的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.33,0:15:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我也理解蕾的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.89,0:15:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是她決定的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.27,0:15:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以想成全她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.54,0:15:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作為一名煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.81,0:15:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前面等待著的會是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.54,0:15:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都生活了幾百年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.42,0:15:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該已經習慣這種事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.21,0:15:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼心緒如此不寧呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.05,0:15:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.32,0:15:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為是酷和蕾吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.58,0:15:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷和蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.24,0:15:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感覺兩人相遇之後萌生了很多很多的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.73,0:15:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以那兩人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.59,0:15:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.39,0:15:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能制止這場戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.20,0:15:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.34,0:15:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帶來一個全新的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.61,0:15:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼想了大家才趕到這裏來的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.46,0:16:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您醒了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.49,0:16:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣一來戰爭就將結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.55,0:16:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後開始一個新的時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.70,0:16:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能遇到酷真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.62,0:16:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.04,0:16:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.27,0:17:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.94,0:17:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.89,0:17:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,退下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.95,0:17:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些傢伙在幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.50,0:17:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.39,0:17:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.03,0:17:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉撒蒂 莉莉雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.72,0:17:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.40,0:17:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已抓住蕾的現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.16,0:17:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嫌同契者礙事是理所當然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.65,0:17:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏交給我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.30,0:17:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.99,0:17:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.73,0:17:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.59,0:17:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終結的福音響起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.04,0:17:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,臥魯克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.96,0:17:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還真不知道居然有獵人不是為錢而戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.32,0:17:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是為我而戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.74,0:17:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,僅此而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.99,0:18:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.11,0:18:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷 沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.71,0:18:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你死了的話就沒臉見蕾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.48,0:18:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.66,0:18:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,命硬的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.12,0:18:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.00,0:18:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我決定去蕾的所在之處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.13,0:18:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.29,0:18:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次一定至死也不離開蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.01,0:18:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.08,0:18:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就看我的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.73,0:18:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.54,0:19:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能飛嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.26,0:19:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,撞得很厲害啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.26,0:19:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過應該能行吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.79,0:19:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,避開 龍威
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.32,0:19:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.30,0:19:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛船穩定不下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.42,0:20:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們所開創的未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.36,0:20:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我見識見識吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.28,0:20:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,臥魯 後面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.79,0:20:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.60,0:20:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,煌珠必須由我們管轄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.96,0:20:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼不明白這一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.46,0:20:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奉命拘捕你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.10,0:20:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必須消滅他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.77,0:20:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,邪惡的並不只是他一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.42,0:20:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恐懼煌珠的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.88,0:20:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宣揚人類至上的思想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.08,0:20:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傷害著煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.78,0:20:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後刀戈相向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.62,0:20:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我們守護者必須一肩承擔的罪孽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.23,0:20:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.29,0:20:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.50,0:20:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們一定...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.91,0:21:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍 龍威
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.25,0:21:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.42,0:21:06.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是約好了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.02,0:21:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帶酷和蕾去煌珠樂園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.49,0:21:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,見到蕾後就不要再分開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.11,0:21:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.24,0:21:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等著我 蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.55,0:21:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在就來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.65,0:22:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那裏有著和平的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.59,0:22:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是現在只剩下悲傷和憤怒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.42,0:22:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下回 煌珠樂園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.43,0:23:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二十四唱 煌珠樂園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.70,0:23:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而少年的生命到頭了

